== Overview ==
The Motion Tracker is a [[:Category:Modules (Utility)|passive module]] that detects and identifies potential targets by their movements and energy signatures. A squad equipped with a Motion Tracker can detect more enemy targets as well as receiving protection from surprise attacks and ambushes.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Motion Tracker can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
